sequenceDiagram
    participant REPL as REPL 组件\n（React）
    participant Bridge as leaderPermissionBridge\n（模块级注册表）
    participant Runner as inProcessRunner\n（非 React）

    REPL->>Bridge: registerLeaderToolUseConfirmQueue(setter)
    REPL->>Bridge: registerLeaderSetToolPermissionContext(setter)
    Note over Bridge: registeredSetter = setter\nregisteredPermissionContextSetter = setter
    Runner->>Bridge: getLeaderToolUseConfirmQueue()
    Bridge-->>Runner: SetToolUseConfirmQueueFn
    Runner->>REPL: 调用 setter → 推入权限对话框
    REPL-->>Runner: 用户决定（Promise resolve）
    Runner->>Bridge: getLeaderSetToolPermissionContext()
    Bridge-->>Runner: SetToolPermissionContextFn
    Runner->>REPL: 调用 setter → 写回权限上下文
    Note over REPL: 组件卸载时 useEffect cleanup
    REPL->>Bridge: unregisterLeaderToolUseConfirmQueue()
    REPL->>Bridge: unregisterLeaderSetToolPermissionContext()
    Note over Bridge: 两个变量重置为 null
